Privacy Policy for Widgets for Stripe
Privacy Policy
Effective Date: October 11, 2024
Widgets for Stripe (“we,” “us,” or “our”) is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our iOS app (“the App”).
1. Information We Collect
Personal Data
We do not collect any personal data.
Non-Personal Data
We may collect
non-personal usage data
to improve the App’s functionality and user experience. This data does not identify you personally and may include anonymized information about how you use the App.
2. Use of Information
The non-personal usage data collected is used solely for the purpose of enhancing and improving the App.
3. Data Sharing
We
do not share any data
with third parties. The Stripe API key you generate to connect your account is a read-only key with limited permissions to your revenue data. We do not have access to your key; it is stored securely on your local device.
4. Children’s Privacy
We do not collect any data from children. If you believe we have inadvertently collected such information, please contact us at
juanjovn@gmail.com
so we can promptly delete it.
5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the new policy in the App, with an updated effective date. Your continued use of the App after any changes signifies your acceptance of the revised Privacy Policy.
6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
juanjovn@gmail.com
.
